 \"Marks just missed out on the podium in Tokyo (where she was the youngest surfer competing) with a fourth-place finish, but won her first world championship last September.\", \"from\": 21957, \"to\": 22128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21996, \"end\": 22001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9380763772983611, \"rank\": 0.06373655097343925, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marks\", \"from\": 21957, \"to\": 21962}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 21982, \"to\": 21992}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest surfer competing\", \"from\": 22017, \"to\": 22046}, {\"ngram\": \"a fourth-place finish\", \"from\": 22053, \"to\": 22074}, {\"ngram\": \"her first world championship\", \"from\": 22084, \"to\": 22112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The titleallowed Marks to reclaim her dominance, having stepped away from the sport in 2022 after feeling the weight of the expectations put upon her since before even starting high school.\", \"from\": 22129, \"to\": 22318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The titleallowed Marks\", \"from\": 22129, \"to\": 22151}, {\"ngram\": \"her dominance\", \"from\": 22163, \"to\": 22176}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 22203, \"to\": 22212}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 22235, \"to\": 22245}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 22249, \"to\": 22265}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 22306, \"to\": 22317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEvery moment away from the tour felt like an eternity,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she toldSports Illustratedin February.\", \"from\": 22319, \"to\": 22418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tour\", \"from\": 22345, \"to\": 22353}, {\"ngram\": \"an eternity\", \"from\": 22364, \"to\": 22375}, {\"ngram\": \"Illustratedin February\", \"from\": 22395, \"to\": 22417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut that made me really focus on what I needed to focus on, and not run away from it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ledecky enters her fourth Olympics looking to dominate in the pool yet again.\", \"from\": 22419, \"to\": 22589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ledecky\", \"from\": 22504, \"to\": 22518}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth Olympics\", \"from\": 22526, \"to\": 22545}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 22569, \"to\": 22577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She came away from both Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2021 as the most decorated female athlete.\", \"from\": 22590, \"to\": 22675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22614, \"end\": 22617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999913914053, \"rank\": 8.60857108363611e-09, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 22627, \"end\": 22632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.989587172582808, \"rank\": 0.010521741921887994, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most decorated female athlete\", \"from\": 22641, \"to\": 22674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The seven-time Olympic champion looks to defend her titles in the 800- and 1500-meter freestyle events, where she is the favorite.\", \"from\": 22676, \"to\": 22806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The seven-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 22676, \"to\": 22707}, {\"ngram\": \"her titles\", \"from\": 22724, \"to\": 22734}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800- and 1500-meter freestyle events\", \"from\": 22738, \"to\": 22778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She holds 29 of the 30 fastest times in the 800 and the top 19 times in the 1500.\", \"from\": 22807, \"to\": 22888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 30 fastest times\", \"from\": 22823, \"to\": 22843}, {\"ngram\": \"the top 19 times\", \"from\": 22859, \"to\": 22875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will be going for an unprecedented fourth straight Olympic title in the 800, the race which kickstarted her Olympic medal haul back in 2012.\", \"from\": 22889, \"to\": 23033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unprecedented fourth straight Olympic title\", \"from\": 22911, \"to\": 22957}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 22970, \"to\": 22978}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic medal haul\", \"from\": 22997, \"to\": 23019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She owns the last five world records in the event and six straight world titles.\\u00c2 Dressel enters his third Olympic Gamesafter taking some time away from the poolfollowing a withdrawal from the 2022 world championships.\", \"from\": 23034, \"to\": 23253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last five world records\", \"from\": 23043, \"to\": 23070}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 23074, \"to\": 23083}, {\"ngram\": \"six straight world titles\", \"from\": 23088, \"to\": 23113}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Dressel\", \"from\": 23114, \"to\": 23123}, {\"ngram\": \"his third Olympic Gamesafter\", \"from\": 23131, \"to\": 23159}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 23167, \"to\": 23176}, {\"ngram\": \"a withdrawal\", \"from\": 23205, \"to\": 23217}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 world championships\", \"from\": 23223, \"to\": 23251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel has only seen the top step of the podium on the Olympic stage, winning seven gold medals between Rio and Tokyo across individual and relay events.\", \"from\": 23254, \"to\": 23408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23359, \"end\": 23362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999913914053, \"rank\": 8.60857108363611e-09, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 23367, \"end\": 23372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.989587172582808, \"rank\": 0.010521741921887994, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 23254, \"to\": 23261}, {\"ngram\": \"the top step\", \"from\": 23276, \"to\": 23288}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 23292, \"to\": 23302}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 23306, \"to\": 23323}, {\"ngram\": \"seven gold medals\", \"from\": 23333, \"to\": 23350}, {\"ngram\": \"individual and relay events\", \"from\": 23380, \"to\": 23407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He narrowly missed out on a spot to qualify for the 100 free but came back to win the 50-meter \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csplash and dash\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d followed by the 100 butterfly on back-to-back nights at U.S. trials in June.\", \"from\": 23409, \"to\": 23602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 23435, \"to\": 23441}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50-meter \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csplash\", \"from\": 23491, \"to\": 23513}, {\"ngram\": \"dash\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 23518, \"to\": 23525}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 23538, \"to\": 23555}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 23567, \"to\": 23571}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. trials\", \"from\": 23582, \"to\": 23593}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 23597, \"to\": 23601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond being a veteran on the U.S. team, Dressel heads to Paris in another role: new father.\", \"from\": 23603, \"to\": 23695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23661, \"end\": 23666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999967493652929, \"rank\": 3.2507403752399365e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"d