 \"from\": 25817, \"to\": 25828}, {\"ngram\": \"performances\", \"from\": 25840, \"to\": 25852}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic team\", \"from\": 25861, \"to\": 25876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago, she won the 50 free in her final chance to secure a spot in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 25878, \"to\": 25961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25955, \"end\": 25960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6709893384749149, \"rank\": 0.49033502560084424, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her final chance\", \"from\": 25918, \"to\": 25934}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 25945, \"to\": 25951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After her triumph, she later revealed that she suffered from overtraining syndrome and was forced to take seven months off from swimming in 2022.\", \"from\": 25962, \"to\": 26107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her triumph\", \"from\": 25968, \"to\": 25979}, {\"ngram\": \"syndrome\", \"from\": 26036, \"to\": 26044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 27-year-old is back, returning to Paris after winning a pair of individual medals\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094gold and silver in Rio\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and a trio of relay medals from Rio and Tokyo.\\u00c2 After a positive test for COVID-19 just days before the Tokyo Games forced her to withdraw, Gauff is ready and focused for her first Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 26108, \"to\": 26425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26150, \"end\": 26155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996571994548, \"rank\": 3.428005946447035e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 26257, \"end\": 26260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res